5
00:00:11,018 --> 00:00:13,664
It's three things at once an operating system

6
00:00:14,048 --> 00:00:16,382
you can boot a laptop into a programming

7
00:00:16,428 --> 00:00:20,015
language called KidLisp and a social network where

8
00:00:20,050 --> 00:00:21,315
