9
00:00:21,699 --> 00:00:24,451
The whole stack is free and open source

10
00:00:24,788 --> 00:00:28,282
Nineteen thousand commits in with seventeen thousand

11
00:00:28,362 --> 00:00:31,289
KidLisp programs and twenty-eight hundred registered

12
00:00:31,335 --> 00:00:35,421
user handles drawing chatting and composing in real

13
00:00:35,479 --> 00:00:35,909
