23
00:01:00,313 --> 00:01:03,912
library a lending fleet of refurbished laptops flashed

24
00:01:04,156 --> 00:01:06,385
with our operating system at fifty dollars per

25
00:01:06,432 --> 00:01:10,472
seat circulating through Flash Days workshops and Family

26
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,329
Play afternoons at the museum.

27
00:01:12,573 --> 00:01:15,906
At the 2027 Symposium we boot the cohort

28
00:01:16,195 --> 00:01:18,819
at the 2028 Demo Day we play the

29
00:01:18,878 --> 00:01:19,353
